#: change-device-name
msgid "Change TV name"
msgstr "Newid enw'r teledu"

#: internetSharing-usb-desc
msgid "Share my TV’s Internet connection with a USB-connected device."
msgstr "Rhannu cysylltiad gwe'r teledu gyda dyfais wedi ei chysylltu drwy USB."

#: internetSharing-wifi-desc
msgid ""
"Allow other devices to share my TV’s Internet connection by connecting via "
"Wi-Fi."
msgstr ""
"Caniatáu i ddyfeisiau eraill rhannu cysylltiad gwe fy nheledu drwy gysylltu "
"drwy'r diwyfr."

#: unplayable-ringtone
msgid ""
"The ringtone was not changed because the selected file can not be played on "
"this TV."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw'r tôn canu wedi newid am nad oedd modd chwarae'r ffeil hon ar y "
"teledu."

#: findmydevice-signup-description
msgid "Find My Device allows you to locate, lock or erase your TV"
msgstr ""
"Mae Canfod Dyfais yn caniatáu i chi ganfod, cloi neu glirio eich teledu"

#: findmydevice-settings-description
msgid ""
"Find My Device allows you to locate, lock or erase your TV from a web site:"
msgstr ""
"Mae Canfod Dyfais yn caniatáu i chi ganfod, cloi neu glirio eich teledu o "
"wefan:"

#: findmydevice-active-tracking
msgid "Your TV is being tracked by another device through the website."
msgstr "Mae eich teledu'n cael ei dracio gan ddyfais arall drwy'r wefan."

#: findmydevice-not-tracking
msgid "No devices are actively tracking your TV through the website."
msgstr "Nid oes dyfeisiau'n tracio eich teledu drwy'r wefan."

#: ums-confirm
msgid ""
"Enabling USB storage allows another computer or device connected using USB "
"to access files on this TV."
msgstr ""
"Mae galluogi storio ar USB yn caniatáu i gyfrifiadur arall neu ddyfais sydd "
"wedi ei chysylltu i gael mynediad i ffeiliau ar y teledu hwn."

#: reset-device
msgid "Reset TV"
msgstr "Ailosod y teledu"

#: reset-warning-body
msgid ""
"Resetting will erase all your data, including any apps you’ve purchased. The "
"TV will be restored to its factory condition. None of your settings or data "
"will be saved."
msgstr ""
"Bydd ailosod yn dileu eich data i gyd, gan gynnwys unrhyw apiau rydych wedi "
"eu prynu. Bydd y teledu yn cael ei adfer i'w gyflwr o'r ffatri. Ni fydd eich "
"gosodiadau na data'n cael eu cadw."

#: powerSave-explanation
msgid ""
"Turning on power save mode turns off the TV’s data, Bluetooth and "
"Geolocation connections to extend battery life. You can still turn these "
"services back on manually."
msgstr ""
"Bydd cychwyn y modd cadw pŵer yn diffodd data, Bluetooth a chysylltiadau "
"geoleoliad y teledu er mwyn estyn oes y batri. Mae modd eu cychwyn eto gyda "
"llaw."

#: performanceAndUsageDataInfo
msgid ""
"Help us improve {{brandShortName}} by sharing data about your TV and the way "
"you use it."
msgstr ""
"Cynorthwywch ni i wella {{brandShortName}} drwy rannu data am eich teledu "
"a'r ffordd rydych yn ei ddefnyddio."

#: device-status-connected-device
msgid "Connected to TV audio"
msgstr "Cysylltu a sain y teledu"

#: device-status-connected-device-media
msgid "Connected to TV/media audio"
msgstr "Cysylltu sain teledu/cyfrwng"
